 ('129', '84', 'en_us', 'Decisions, decisions, decisions...', '<p>Big Day last Thursday... we were tasting and trying to decide on final blends for next fall\'s releases -- which percentages of which grapes we like best for which bottling -- knowing that the possibilities are infinite! It sounds like fun but it\'s actually a difficult exercise and the worst part is that  one has to spit the wine out ! here in the picture the team: Enzo, Valentino our oenologist and Roberto.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-04-14 14:34:12', '2015-04-16 10:18:50', 'ea350151-a388-4861-9fd1-c90770535717'),
