 ('141', '91', 'en_us', 'What to do in the winter in a vineyard? Pruning... ', '<p>\r\n	 What do you do in the winter in a vineyard? Prune... here are some pictures from the pruning work underway. We\'re no way finished yet, it\'s quite slow going but ever so important. How we prune now will influence how the vines will grow over time and how the fruit will develop over the next two consecutive years.\r\n</p><p>\r\n	<img style=\"width: 600px; height: 336.94px;\" src=\"{asset:89:url}\" unselectable=\"on\"><br>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-04-14 15:51:08', '2015-04-16 13:23:36', '8f9c94cd-c040-49da-8a11-61e7326198d7'),
 ('142', '92', 'en_us', 'Sun Valley Anyone? ', '<p>Anyone going to be in Sun Valley Idaho on February 27th? If yes, try to go to CK\'s yearly special Italian dinner, starring Poggio La Noce wines. and as a bonus Enzo will be there too!</p><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-04-14 15:57:34', '2015-04-16 12:59:21', 'e01ea686-b834-45c5-9a07-a99a6e88276c'),
