t year\'s two year old cane. Only tweak is us doing \\\"double\\\" or \\\"bilateral\\\" meaning that we allow for two 2 year old canes, one on each side.<\\/p><p> That\'s the world of vine pruning in the winter time at La Noce!<\\/p>\",\"25\":[\"109\"],\"2\":\"\"}}', '2015-04-16 11:03:25', '2015-04-16 11:03:25', 'a208093a-9de1-4a08-8ff4-38465d8e2e71'),
