 ('173', '82', '2', '1', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Astor Grand Tasting Wine Event\",\"slug\":\"astor-grand-tasting-wine-event\",\"postDate\":1429021320,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\tFor all the New Yorkers out there -- or anyone else who will be in New York city this Saturday, April 18th, do come and check out \\\"Astor\'s Grand Tasting\\\" event, where yours truly \\\"Poggio La Noce\\\" has been invited to participate. \\r\\n\\t<br>\\r\\n\\t It should be a great event, they\'ve invited only artisan winemakers or as they say \\\"foremost artisan winemakers\\\", 13 wineries and will be serving current releases as well as older vintages. And I forgot the best, Enzo will be there to pour our wines!\\r\\n\\t<br>\\r\\n\\t Time 11.00am to 3.00pm. Place Astor Center. <\\/p><p>\\r\\n\\t<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.astorcenternyc.com\\/winemakers-invitational\\/default.aspx?ref=hp\\\">Astor Center New York City link<\\/a>\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"25\":[\"104\"],\"2\":\"\"}}', '2015-04-16 13:18:54', '2015-04-16 13:18:54', '4d43158e-f8f6-4b25-931e-6051fffe0d54');
