 ('473', '48', '3', '1', 'en_us', '28', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Contact\",\"slug\":\"contact\",\"postDate\":1421257560,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"8\":{\"49\":{\"type\":\"banner\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"bannerHeadline\":\"Get in touch\",\"bannerImage\":[\"73\"]}}},\"7\":\"<h2>How to reach us<\\/h2>\\r\\n<iframe src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d58129.93243744846!2d11.370236447956291!3d43.78779223369125!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x132baad566a47839%3A0x37a833dd8b34d006!2sPoggio+La+Noce!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1478811195558\\\" width=\\\"900\\\" height=\\\"450\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border:0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"\\\"><\\/iframe>\\r\\n<p>Using Googlemap enter \\\"Poggio La Noce\\\".<br>Otherwise reach the village of Montebeni, Fiesole. Once there, follow Via Ontignano till the bottom of the valley. When you reach the unpaved section of the road, the road climbs for roughly two hundred yards, after which you will see the entrance to the estate with a sign \\\"Poggio La Noce\\\".&nbsp;If you need assistance, please call us at 055 654 9113.<br>GPS coordinates: Lat. 43.796735, Long. 11.345128.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Winery Visits<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>The New Poggio La Noce winery is open for visits and tastings, just 15 minutes from the center of Florence!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Poggio La Noce is a small, intimate wine estate and we offer a unique and personal tasting experience. The visit will include a walk through our vineyard as well as a tour of our brand new winery.&nbsp; The visit will be followed by a tasting of all our wines accompanied with light snacks.&nbsp; Cost of the visit and tasting: 15 Euro per person.&nbsp; <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>By appointment only, so please email or call us before hand.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Email Us<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Contact us by filling out the following information<br><\\/p>\",\"12\":[\"75\",\"332\"],\"6\":\"Contact us\",\"26\":{\"331\":{\"type\":\"photoGallery\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"galleryTitle\":\"Winery Visits and Tastings\",\"galleryDescription\":\"Visitors at Poggio La Noce\",\"galleryImages\":[\"327\",\"328\",\"329\",\"330\",\"326\"],\"galleryPageInclude\":\"1\"}}}}}', '2016-12-06 20:57:00', '2016-12-06 20:57:00', '92530db8-fcf5-45db-9757-720ef5eaf6c4'),
 ('474', '48', '3', '1', 'it', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Contatti\",\"slug\":\"contact\",\"postDate\":1421257560,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"8\":{\"49\":{\"type\":\"banner\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"bannerHeadline\":\"Contatti\",\"bannerImage\":[\"73\"]}}},\"7\":\"<h2>Come raggiungerci<\\/h2>\\r\\n<iframe src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d58129.93243744846!2d11.370236447956291!3d43.78779223369125!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x132baad566a47839%3A0x37a833dd8b34d006!2sPoggio+La+Noce!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1478811195558\\\" width=\\\"900\\\" height=\\\"450\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border:0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"\\\"><\\/iframe>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Utilizzando googlemap, inserire Poggio La Noce.<br>Altrimenti arrivare nel paese di Montebeni (Fiesole). Seguendo Via Ontignano, continuare fino in fondo alla valle. Una volta giunti all\'inizio della strada sterrata continuare a salire per circa 200 metri e troverete il cartello con la scritta \\\"Poggio La Noce\\\", l\\u2019ingresso dell\\u2019azienda. Se avete bisogno di Assistenza chiamateci al 055 654 91 13.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Coordinate GPS: Lat. 43.796735, Long. 11.345128.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Visita in Cantina<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Nel cuore di Fiesole, a due passi da Firenze, potrete scoprire una piccola azienda vitivinicola, completamente biologica e gestita in modo del tutto artigianale. Visiterete il nostro vigneto che e parte integrante della propriet\\u00e0 ed avrete modo di capire - visitando la nostra nuova cantina - come la nostra metodologia di vinificazione ci permette di arrivare ad un prodotto sano, di altissima qualit\\u00e0 ma soprattutto che&nbsp;\\u00e8 una gioia bere! La visita sar\\u00e0 seguita da una degustazione di&nbsp;tutti i nostri&nbsp;vini.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I costo e di 15 \\u20ac a persona, solo su prenotazione. Per prenotare, chiamateci o contatteci per email.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Contatteci per email<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Contatteci fornendoci le seguenti informazioni<\\/p>\",\"12\":[\"75\",\"332\"],\"6\":\"Venite a trovarci\",\"26\":{\"331\":{\"type\":\"photoGallery\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"galleryTitle\":\"Cantina visita e degustazione\",\"galleryDescription\":\"Visite nella nuova cantina di Poggio La Noce\",\"galleryImages\":[\"327\",\"328\",\"329\",\"330\",\"326\"],\"galleryPageInclude\":\"1\"}}}}}', '2016-12-06 20:58:04', '2016-12-06 20:58:04', '08607a04-23e8-433b-b331-cb0584cb9976');
