 ('218', 'field', '13', 'en_us', ' we think of it as the little brother of gigio it is a wine of surprising immediacy while still offering plenty of experiences to the nose and palate gigetto was born out of our own wish to drink a pleasant genuine wine yet with exceptional fruit and easier drinkability gigetto is released a year earlier than gigio and typically ages in large size botte only a few months '),
